description: Two of my best friends and Jazz drumming legends Peter Erskine & Adam Nussbaum, join me for a fun chat about drums, cymbals, music, road stories and life. Peter talks about his career working with Steely Dan, Weather Report and Maynard Ferguson. This was so much fun!
channel: John DeChristopher - Live From My Drum Room
fulltitle: Episode 5: Live From My Drum Room: Peter Erskine & Adam Nussbaum - May 13, 2020
